🎯 Student Goal Tracker

This is a simple and interactive Goal Tracking Web App built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Firebase (Firestore + Authentication).
It allows users (students) to register, log in, add goals, mark them as completed, and track progress through a star-based reward system ⭐.

✅ Features

🔐 User Authentication (Register & Login)

📝 Add daily/weekly/monthly goals

☑ Mark goals as completed with checkboxes

⭐ Live star count updates based on completed goals

❌ Delete goals individually

🔄 Persistent goal storage using Firebase Firestore

🎨 Clean, user-friendly dashboard layout


🚀 Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Backend/Database: Firebase Authentication, Firestore Database
